data.description: Beautiful updated 4 bedroom, 3 bathroom home in a cul-de-sac on a nice large lot with backyard access! Master bedroom and bedroom 2 are on the main floor, bedroom 3 and 4 are on the upper level.  This home features ALL NEW: paint, carpet, stainless steel appliances, granite, vanities and sinks, faucets, lighting, fixtures and hardware. All new windows being installed 8/20 or sooner.
